    "name": "猫岛雨香",
    "steam_appid": 3181890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「解开漂浮在平静海面上的猫岛谜团」</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/fba715846d87e9e5b714e570587d49e6.avif?t=1771864223\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徜徉在大海上的小岛，猫咪们的乐园──「猫岛」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学生「白水真」受到这座神秘岛屿所吸引，从外面​​的世界前来追寻真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将化身为住在猫岛上的一只白猫，钻进狭窄的缝隙，或是轻巧地跳上高处……发挥这些猫咪独有的灵活本领，协助真进行调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真所追寻的猫岛谜团究竟是什么──</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场既温馨疗愈，却又带着一抹哀愁的3D探索冒险，正在等着您！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「发挥猫咪独有的灵活动作在猫岛上探险」</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/1dbd69f2063e14e32f68b01ee054fcd6.avif?t=1771864223\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以多样化的猫咪动作，协助真展开调查！例如磨爪开路、跳上屋顶，或是来一场速度竞赛……等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥猫咪的机智，来突破重重机关吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/20387ba8959f9e2aa6aa732a42eec6c9.avif?t=1771864223\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫岛由5大区域，共18张地图构成。包含岛上休息站、神社、灯台、资料馆、遗迹、医院……等多样化的场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，随着时间流逝与天气变化，岛屿将呈现不同面貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境丰富多变的猫岛，正静候您的到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「融合3D与2D，魅力十足的女主角们」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/6d482874ff0f25a4d67aa9bac3086165.avif?t=1771864223\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以自由探索的3D空间体验，结合2D角色对话演出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话事件采用了Spine动画技术，让角色们的动作栩栩如生，演绎出表情丰富的互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共收录26张CG（包含差分共72张）！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以丰富插画为您在岛上的体验增添缤纷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/4a1dc608b2e20b39703c4e2cdbe92482.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>白水真</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV 美凪ゆう</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造访猫岛追寻谜团的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性温柔又开朗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然朋友众多又人见人爱，但也是能享受独处的类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平易近人，具备很强的沟通能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于喜欢的事物有着很强的学习热忱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/c9bc65bf87aa437d8cce4706b2f3431d.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小白</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >居住在充满猫咪的岛上的白猫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以港口周边为地盘，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天过着在防波堤远眺大海的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造访岛屿的真为它取名叫「小白」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将操作小白，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协助真进行调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/d8a818aa23d25d1851d4819e7feae119.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美樱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV 宇佐木りこ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食堂的独生女，是岛上无人不知的看板娘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格大方又充满活力，很容易亲近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成天不是在玩耍就是在发呆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与母亲的关系良好，称呼其为「妈妈」并仰慕着她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/f0b266abea8e16ddbaa2baba30e81c43.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美月</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV 咲橙英玲な</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营食堂的老板娘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对初次见面的人或不熟悉的环境时容易紧张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营的食堂是所有岛民的休憩场所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与女儿感情很好，关系就像朋友一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/69c28b1f9510ddd6eee0133bb970a1ce.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>静流</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV 纯夏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上神社的巫女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格沉稳且冷静。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对初次见面的人话不多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有着一丝不苟的一面，勤于打扫神社境内。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平时会在食堂用餐，与镇民们关系良好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/65b03c9395016ae1f801f3a8a6b76213.avif?t=1771864223\" width=600 height=745 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诗叶</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV 紫咲そら</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在岛上休息站担任接待员的女生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文静且沉默寡言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格非常我行我素，很重视独处的时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对他人不太感兴趣，不怎么擅长与人来往。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏内容</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分为5大区域，共18张地图（包含散布在区域内的建筑内部等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5位女主角</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含与第二女主角的交流剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话事件：共214个以上（包含大小事件）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文本：共15万字以上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语音：共265分钟以上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spine动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >表情差分：共10种以上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服装、动作差分</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG：共26张（包含差分共72张）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时间：6～12小时</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对应语言：日语、英语、简体中文、繁体中文、西班牙语、韩语</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※在制作过程中，有部分贴图修正使用了AI技术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※本作包含精神状态不稳定的角色，以及可能导致强烈不安或不适的表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
